## `.env` File (Warning: Change these before production use!)

**The environment variables below contain default credentials and tokens. Ensure you change the sensitive information, especially passwords and tokens, before running the stack in production.**

```
DOCKER_INFLUXDB_INIT_MODE=setup

# Primary InfluxDB admin/superuser credentials
DOCKER_INFLUXDB_INIT_USERNAME=gs4162
DOCKER_INFLUXDB_INIT_PASSWORD=changepassword
DOCKER_INFLUXDB_INIT_ADMIN_TOKEN=7403ACF9E98B1021D8343479A9BDF402

# Primary InfluxDB Telegraf config
DOCKER_INFLUXDB_MQTT_USER=gs4162
DOCKER_INFLUXDB_MQTT_PASSWORD=changepassword

# Primary InfluxDB organization & bucket definitions
DOCKER_INFLUXDB_INIT_ORG=MHM 
DOCKER_INFLUXDB_INIT_BUCKET=siteexample

# Primary InfluxDB bucket retention period
DOCKER_INFLUXDB_INIT_RETENTION=4d 

